Welcome to The Worlds Longest Website!
The creator is sorry for using high usage of storage. Please scroll carefully as this may affect your device.
For your safety, this website is considered safe and contains no viruses.

About this game:
The Worlds Longest Website is a website that is very long in terms of pixels (about 30 million flat)
The only thing you could do is to:
Scroll. That. Wheel.
Good luck, as this may take hours or even days.

V2.0

wow :0 you came here? thats awesome!

Wow, its becoming dusty in 


Well, not that

Long ago, you started this journey, Just to scroll for hours or even days. Keep up! As you are going to approach the end. Milestone check! 1.25 million lines.
Achievement unlocked: The One
